Oct 2019 • Friends
The cruising and boat during through Halong Bay is a magical, scenic and picturesque experience. Photos honestly don't do this place justice! A sunset here was an experience I'll remember for a life time.
The only negative is in some parts the water was populated and dirty was was a downer.... We need to preserve this place!!
