Traveller162014
Leeds, UK1,037 contributions
Beautiful Place
Nov 2022
This is definitely one of the most beautiful places I have ever been and a must do if you're in Vietnam because it genuinely is stunning. We did a 1 night cruise (forgive me, I can't remember the name of it) and the views were astonishing, and it was great going to a little island for a swim and some boat jumping. We also did kayaking and again, the best views I've ever experienced when kayaking.
The only downside is, as some other reviewers have mentioned, the rubbish. I wouldn't go as far as to say it ruined the experience but there was a bit more pollution than I thought. I only really noticed it when kayaking though and it wasn't ALL OVER it was just in certain bits. Thing is, though, that's the reality of our world isn't it. Humans have managed to damage even the most beautiful places.
Written December 6, 2022
